short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: An extension for https://supermemory.ai - an AI hub for all your knowledge.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Supermemory is an AI tool that enables you to have "SuperMemory" of everything you save - Blogs, whether it's blogs, videos, or any other website.

You can also talk to the contents of the current website to find things and supercharge your workflow.
